## Quick Start

### 1. Environment Setup (Recommended)

Create a `.env` file in your project root:

```env
{PACKAGE_NAME_UPPER}_BASE_URL=https://your-api.com
{PACKAGE_NAME_UPPER}_API_KEY=your-secure-api-key
```

### 2. Initialize the SDK

```typescript
import { Configuration, DefaultApi } from '{PACKAGE_NAME}';
import { createConfig, EnvCredentialProvider } from '{PACKAGE_NAME}/config';

// Option 1: Using environment variables (RECOMMENDED)
const config = new Configuration(createConfig());
const api = new DefaultApi(config);

// Option 2: Using credential provider
const config = new Configuration(createConfig({
  credentialProvider: new EnvCredentialProvider()
}));
const api = new DefaultApi(config);

// Option 3: Direct configuration (NOT recommended for production)
const config = new Configuration({
  basePath: 'https://your-api.com',
  apiKey: 'your-api-key' // ⚠️ Never hardcode in production!
