The SDK supports multiple authentication strategies:

#### Environment Variables (Recommended)
```typescript
import { EnvCredentialProvider } from '{PACKAGE_NAME}/config';

const provider = new EnvCredentialProvider();
const config = createConfig({ credentialProvider: provider });
```

#### Static Credentials (Testing Only)
```typescript
import { StaticCredentialProvider } from '{PACKAGE_NAME}/config';

const provider = new StaticCredentialProvider('your-api-key');
const config = createConfig({ credentialProvider: provider });
```

#### Custom Provider (Advanced)
```typescript
import { CredentialProvider } from '{PACKAGE_NAME}/config';

class KeyVaultProvider implements CredentialProvider {
  async getApiKey() {
    // Fetch from Azure Key Vault, AWS Secrets Manager, etc.
    return await fetchFromKeyVault('my-api-key');
  }
}

const provider = new KeyVaultProvider();
const config = createConfig({ credentialProvider: provider });
```

